# game/day 9.rpy:628
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_207cae7b:

    # "So, I was happy to go out for a walk.{p}With weather like this,\nit's much easier to go outside."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 39)
