# game/day 9.rpy:629
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_36ad0847:

    # "Usually, I'd be shrivelling to a crisp,\ncomplaining about it being so hot.\nSo today I jumped at the chance to go out."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 43)
