    # ka "「What are you doing, way out here?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 231)
    ka "【洸哉】\n「你在这种地方干什么呢？」"

# game/day 9.rpy:713
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_b77b0cf9:

    # fn "「...You scared me.{p} Don't surprise me like that, Kouya.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 233)
    fn "【fn！「——你把我吓到了。[l]别吓唬我啊，洸哉。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:717
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_b7f20602:

    # ka "「I wasn't trying to surprise you.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 239)
    ka "【洸哉】\n「我才没想要吓你。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:718
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_291d1e8a:

    # fn "「...Oh well, I won't get anywhere,\n sweating the small stuff like this.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 241)
    fn "【fn！「……好吧，斤斤计较的话[漏水]就输了。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:722
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_9ef8e76d:

    # ka "「Saying that in advance for something, huh.{p} So,{w=.3} what was that about \"no good at all\" earlier?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 244)
    ka "【洸哉】\n「跟之前你说的一样嘛。[l]那么，[wdt]你前面说『糟糕透了』是在指什么？」"

# game/day 9.rpy:723
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_cb42cd7e:

    # "As he asked, he sat down beside me."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 249)
    "他边问边坐到了[漏水]的身边。"

# game/day 9.rpy:724
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_065b8840:

    # fn "「Hmm?{p} I just can't remember something from a while back.{p} Have I really gotten so old?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 251)
    fn "【fn！「呃？[l][漏水]不过只是记不起来以前的事了。[l]这样的话，是[漏水]真的变得那么老了么？」"

# game/day 9.rpy:728
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_8e40c28d:

    # ka "「Yeah, you're old enough.{p} Thinking is what middle-aged people do.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 258)
    ka "【洸哉】\n「是啊，你这起码已经老了十岁吧。[l]思考是中年人的专利。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:729
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_b0d2a16e:

    # fn "「...Can't you play along better than that?{p} I was waiting for a straight man just now, you know?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 262)
    fn "【fn！「……你就不能合作下吗？[l][漏水]现在需要一个捧哏，理解了吗？」"

# game/day 9.rpy:730
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_b2181f9b:

    # ka "「Sorry, I don't think I'd be a very good\n straight man. I'll pass.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 267)
    ka "【洸哉】\n「真抱歉，我不认为我有能成为优秀捧哏的天赋，于是我就放弃了。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:731
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_093fc40b:

    # fn "「You're so cold.{w} By the way,\n what were you doing out here in the rain?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 269)
    fn "【fn！「真是过分。[l]不过话说回来这么大的雨，你在这里做什么？」"

# game/day 9.rpy:735
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_740c6637:

    # ka "「I was out doing some shopping.{p} When I came out of the store, it was raining,\n so I was running, when I passed by someone I knew.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 275)
    ka "【洸哉】\n「我出门买东西。[l]但是从商店里出来之后，就开始下雨了。所以我就开始全速的开始跑，路上还遇上了一个我认识的人。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:739
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_a5ac82fe:

    # ka "「I wondered what you were doing, you know?{p} So I tried following you.{p} Then I noticed this place.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 281)
    ka "【洸哉】\n「我当时就很好奇的​​在想『他打算去哪？』[l]所以就跟在你后面了。[l]再之后我就想到了这个地方。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:740
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_dbe3da63:

    # fn "「I-{w=.3}is that so...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 288)
    fn "【fn！「哦，[wdt]原来如此……」"

# game/day 9.rpy:741
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_c702fc6a:

    # "He saw everything, then.{p}I wanna die from embarrassment."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 290)
    "所以说，他完全的看到了淋湿的[漏水]。[l]现在[漏水]该考虑努力的找个地缝了。"

# game/day 9.rpy:745
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_8eb01823:

    # ka "「Hey, that's what I should be asking.{p} So what are you doing, out on this kind of day?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 294)
    ka "【洸哉】\n「不过那个问题我也想问问你。[l]你出门是干什么呢？这种天气。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:746
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_fd147890:

    # fn "「Hm?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 298)
    fn "【fn！「嗯？」"

# game/day 9.rpy:750
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_d63392c8:

    # ka "「The forecast said there'd be rain today,\n so why would you go out loitering empty-handed?\n ...That's what I'm asking you.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 301)
    ka "【洸哉】\n「天气预报有说今天会下雨，所以说为什么你两手空空的在外头逛？――这就是我想问的了。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:751
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_69ce35dd:

    # fn "「Aah...{w} I missed out on the forecast.{p} If I hadn't I wouldn't be out here, pretty much.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 307)
    fn "【fn！「啊啊……[l]天气预报的话[漏水]是错过了。如果没有错过[漏水]也不会在这里，差不多就是这样。"

# game/day 9.rpy:752
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_d71f1981:

    # ka "「Oh you...\n make sure of these things when you go out.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 314)
    ka "【洸哉】\n「是这样啊……这些事的话出门前得确认好啊。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:753
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_bc53d0ca:

    # ka "「Give me a break.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 316)
    ka "「真是的……」洸哉一边揺头一边说。"

# game/day 9.rpy:754
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_281b75e4:

    # "Kouya shook his head and took a deep sigh."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 318)
    "【fn！「[漏水]也是那么想的……但是呢，早上还是晴天对吧？之前也是。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:755
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_42538f30:

    # fn "「I was thinking that too...\n But still, it was clear this morning.\n It *was* clear, wasn't it?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 323)
    fn "【洸哉】\n「是啊，是个晴天。[l]包括早上天气都是十分光朗，看着就是个好天气。[l]但是这跟之后的天气没有任何关系。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:756
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_a84318a7:

    # ka "「Yeah yeah, it was.{p} It was all clear, looking like good weather.{p} But that doesn't have an effect on weather later on.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 328)
    ka "【fn！「[漏水]当然知道的。[漏水]想那个晴天还会持续下去的……」"

# game/day 9.rpy:757
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_93977549:

    # fn "「Hahahah, I know right?\n But, if only it kept that way...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 323-326)
    fn "【洸哉】「是啊，是个晴天。[l]包括早上天气都是十分晴朗，光看着就是个好天气。[l]但是这跟之后的天气没有任何关系。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:758
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_9350cb80:

    # "After saying that, I got depressed.\nUnintentionally, I let out a sigh."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 336)
    "【洸哉】\n「真是的……」"

# game/day 9.rpy:759
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_82f187a5:

    # ka "「Geez...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 336)
    ka "【洸哉】「真是的……」"

# game/day 9.rpy:760
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_f6909ed0:

    # "When he saw me like that,\nit seemed as if he were surprised."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 340)
    "不，与其用「似乎」来描述不如用「确实」来描述。后者更加贴切。"

# game/day 9.rpy:761
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_b7081dac:

    # "Wait, it's less \"seemed as\" and\nmore \"actually\" surprised."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 343)
    "【洸哉】\n「……​​呐。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:765
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_6c4df4e0:

    # ka "「...Hey.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 345)
    ka "【fn！「嗯？[wdt]怎么？」"

# game/day 9.rpy:766
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_5ff5828d:

    # fn "「Mm,{w=.3} what?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 351)
    fn "【洸哉】\n「在出门之后你做了什么吗？」"

# game/day 9.rpy:767
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_3c2df731:

    # ka "「You doing anything after this?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 353)
    ka "【fn！「没有，[漏水]只是想出来散步，只要回家里就可以了。[l]但这场雨……」"

# game/day 9.rpy:768
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_5bfbaf84:

    # fn "「No, I was out on a simple walk,\n then I was thinking it'd be nice to go home.{p} But there's the rain and all...」"
    # [原版缩写] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 358)
    fn "[漏水]边说边抬头仰望着天空。"

# game/day 9.rpy:769
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_35429170:

    # "While I was speaking, I looked up into the sky."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 360)
    "天空仍是浑浊的深铅灰色。说真的，[漏水]觉得这灰色的云已经变不淡了。"

# game/day 9.rpy:770
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_731cc20b:

    # "The sky was still shaded in lead.\nThough honestly, the color of lead\nalready looks like it wouldn't water down."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 363)
    "如果没有伞，难以想象[漏水]要如何能在这场雨中回家。"

# game/day 9.rpy:771
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_f94e6909:

    # "Without an umbrella,\nI can't think about going back in this."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 367)
    "【洸哉】\n「我知道了，也就是说只要你有伞就可以回去了。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:775
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_cecc4c69:

    # ka "「I see, so if you had an umbrella you could go back.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 369)
    ka "【fn！「就是这样。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:776
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_de7b49bf:

    # fn "「That's how it is.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 374)
    fn "【洸哉】\n「现在就回吗？」"

# game/day 9.rpy:780
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_8ee1500f:

    # ka "「Wanna go back, then?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 376)
    ka "【fn！「诶――？」"

# game/day 9.rpy:781
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_1e5bd7e9:

    # fn "「Eh?」"
    # [原版缩写] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 378)
    fn "似乎完全没有听到[漏水]疑惑的声音，洸哉站了起来。"

# game/day 9.rpy:782
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_82a0ef32:

    # "Kouya stood up as if he hadn't heard a thing I said."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 382)
    "【fn！「呃，[wdt][漏水]想[漏水]们会被淋成落汤鸡的吧。[l]而且伞呢？」"

# game/day 9.rpy:783
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_7537e91a:

    # fn "「Eh,{w=.3} but we'll get all soaked.{p} And what about an umbrella?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 386)
    fn "【洸哉】\n「你说什么呢？[l]伞的话我这里不就有一把么？」"

# game/day 9.rpy:787
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_340435e2:

    # ka "「What are you talking about?{p} I've got an umbrella.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 389)
    ka "【fn！「啊――」"

# game/day 9.rpy:788
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_d050ca7b:

    # fn "「Ah...」"
    # [原版缩写] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 393)
    fn "[漏水]往下看去，洸哉的手里拿着一把蓝绿色的雨伞。"

# game/day 9.rpy:789
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_2169b9a3:

    # "I looked down,\nand there in Kouya's hand was a blue-green umbrella."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 397)
    "起先他和[漏水]在雨中擦肩而过，但他身上一点也没有淋湿。"

# game/day 9.rpy:790
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_a21b25da:

    # "He passed by me in the rain in the first place,\nbut he isn't wet at all."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 400)
    "【fn！「嗯……[l][漏水]也这么想的。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:791
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_921b25bd:

    # fn "「Oh...{w} I see then.」"
    # [原版缩写] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 403)
    fn "因为被雨淋，[漏水]的脾气有点暴躁了。这样的事直到他说出来了[漏水]才注意到。"

# game/day 9.rpy:792
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_f2500e23:

    # "I was in a temper from being soaked in the rain,\nand I didn't notice until he pointed it out."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 406)
    "这还这是相当要命的一种感觉啊。"

# game/day 9.rpy:793
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_d5e82d2b:

    # "I really am feeling like I'll drop dead..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 408)
    "【洸哉】\n「你的观察能力要锻炼呢。[l]可以走了吧？」"

# game/day 9.rpy:794
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_824ce1c3:

    # ka "「Your ability to notice things really is weak...{p} Oh well, shall we go?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 413)
    ka "【洸哉 hide こすり][wt]\n「砰」的一声，雨伞被打开了。[l]伞上美丽的色彩"

# game/day 9.rpy:799
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_b96e0d78:

    # "With a *fwump*, the umbrella opened.{p}The beautiful hue reminded me\nof an illusionary flower blooming from somewhere."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 417)
    "就象是幻想之中的花朵绽放一般。"

# game/day 9.rpy:800
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_f77b3094:

    # "A very mysterious flower,\nwith curled up leaves and no petals."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 419)
    "叶子优雅的卷起，没有花瓣。这是一朵不可思议的花朵。"

# game/day 9.rpy:804
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_6fc9d157_1:

    # fn "「...?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 423)
    fn "【fn！「……？」"

# game/day 9.rpy:805
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_47f6e0c6:

    # "In the moment I saw that,\nsomething flickered in my field of vision."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 426)
    "就在这个时候，[漏水]看到了。从视野里闪过。"

# game/day 9.rpy:806
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_3258eb92:

    # "Huh, where did I...?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 428)
    "嗯，[漏水]在哪里……？"

# game/day 9.rpy:807
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_ef0b3c7e:

    # "Somewhere in my head, I could hear a whisper."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 430)
    "在[漏水]脑海中的某一处，听到了一个低语着的声音。"

# game/day 9.rpy:808
translate chinese_simplified kouya09_61db36a7:

    # "Do I know this...?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/洸哉_s_04.ks (KS 432)
