translate chinese_simplified shin09_cpr_e99fff2a:

    # fn "「Eh?{w} Yeah, that's true.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 深_m_03.ks (KS 1165-1165)
    fn "「为什么，这个，」"

# game/day 9.rpy:1819
translate chinese_simplified shin09_cpr_766cc25c:

    # si "「That's why it's fine.{p} It's peaceful yet noisy,\n so I can really relax.」"
    # [原版缩写] 来源: 深_m_03.ks (KS 1167-1169)
    si "似乎他还有点混乱的样子。[l]像是要从[漏れ]身边逃走似的跳了开来，接着突然就开始质问了起来。"

# game/day 9.rpy:1823
translate chinese_simplified shin09_cpr_53345107:

    # "It's peaceful,\nbut if you listen closely you can hear so much."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 深_m_03.ks (KS 1172-1174)
    "「因为看到深君走进了森林，有点担心就跟在后面看看，[l]然后发现深君倒在这里。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:1824
translate chinese_simplified shin09_cpr_5c438a97:

    # "The wood shaking in the winds,{w} insect buzzing,{p}and then, that vaguely familiar, annoying tinnying."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 深_m_03.ks (KS 1177-1179)
    "「不过，看来好像没事的样子。[l]太好了。[wdt]刚看到的时候真的紧张到心脏都差点要跳出来了说。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:1825
translate chinese_simplified shin09_cpr_68d10cf2:

    # fn "「Ah! Dammit!」"
    # [原版缩写] 来源: 深_m_03.ks (KS 1184-1186)
    fn "深君的声音更大了。[l]呜呜，[wdt]跟平常一样这点虽然让人很高兴，但[漏れ]可是真的非常担心的说。"

# game/day 9.rpy:1829
translate chinese_simplified shin09_cpr_e33b90f9:

    # si "「What's wrong?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 深_m_03.ks (KS 1189-1190)
    si "「不、不过是要撞到了头的话，还是去检查一下比较好……」"

# game/day 9.rpy:1830
translate chinese_simplified shin09_cpr_2cd6d2ee:

    # fn "「A bug bit me.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 深_m_03.ks (KS 1202-1202)
    fn "「看来，你似乎完全误解了的样子。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:1831
translate chinese_simplified shin09_cpr_a077ff9a:

    # "When I checked myself again,\nI must have been bitten\nso many times on the way here."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 深_m_03.ks (KS 1218-1218)
    "「只是在睡觉！？」"

# game/day 9.rpy:1832
translate chinese_simplified shin09_cpr_51d04c4b:

    # "My arms, my neck, my back,\n{w=.3}just about everywhere."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 深_m_03.ks (KS 1221-1221)
    "「……[l][深 不満、赤面 リュック normal]」"

# game/day 9.rpy:1836
translate chinese_simplified shin09_cpr_5588bc01:

    # si "「[fn], you didn't use any repellant,\n did you?」"
    # [原版缩写] 来源: 深_m_03.ks (KS 1223-1223)
    si "这个，也就是说，[wdt]深君只是在这里睡午觉而已吗？"

# game/day 9.rpy:1837
translate chinese_simplified shin09_cpr_d1b2b527:

    # fn "「That's because I didn't think\n I'd be going into the forest.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 深_m_03.ks (KS 1226-1226)
    fn "「可是，怎么会把那个背包当成枕头……」"

# game/day 9.rpy:1841
translate chinese_simplified shin09_cpr_88034ddd:

    # si "「Oh whatever. {w=.3}I'll get you some medicine later.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 深_m_03.ks (KS 1229-1230)
    si "「虽然也有放别的东西，但已经用毛巾包起来了所以没问题。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:1842
translate chinese_simplified shin09_cpr_caabba0d:

    # fn "「Dammit, here too!?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 深_m_03.ks (KS 1233-1233)
    fn "「……[l]为什么在这里睡啊？」"

# game/day 9.rpy:1846
translate chinese_simplified shin09_cpr_b7c5cfa1:

    # "Shin-kun watched and laughed as I\nchecked myself over again."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 深_m_03.ks (KS 1244-1244)
    "「我想在哪里睡觉跟你没有关系吧！」"

# game/day 9.rpy:1850
translate chinese_simplified shin09_cpr_92604f68:

    # si "「Well then,{w=.3} I suppose it's time to go home.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 深_m_03.ks (KS 1247-1247)
    si "「是！[wdt] 你说的没错。对不起。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:1851
translate chinese_simplified shin09_cpr_b532c752:

    # fn "「Oh, sure.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 深_m_03.ks (KS 1253-1254)
    fn "「不，抱歉。[l]我也知道就算跟你大吼也没用。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:1852
translate chinese_simplified shin09_cpr_3df50741:

    # si "「Sorry about today.{w=.3} It looks like\n it's my fault you're flapping like that.{p} {nw}"
    # [原版缩写] 来源: 深_m_03.ks (KS 1256-1257)
    si "深君像是要让自己冷静下来似地，摇了摇头之后深深吸了口气。"

# game/day 9.rpy:1854
translate chinese_simplified shin09_cpr_f1b2b157:

    # extend "Would you like to come over later?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 深_m_03.ks (KS 1263-1264)
    extend "「……[l]以前，[wdt]我曾经在别的地方像这样子在睡午觉。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:1855
translate chinese_simplified shin09_cpr_ca8aaf49:

    # fn "「Huh?{w=.3} Is that okay?」"
    # [原版缩写] 来源: 深_m_03.ks (KS 1266-1267)
    fn "睡午觉，[wdt]也就是说，是有先做好准备，想好好地睡个觉的意思吗……"

# game/day 9.rpy:1856
translate chinese_simplified shin09_cpr_62f75d08:

    # si "「Yeah.{p} I want to treat you to a lunch,{w=.3}\n {nw}"
    # [原版缩写] 来源: 深_m_03.ks (KS 1269-1271)
    si "刚刚因为慌张的关系没注意到，但其实草地上有铺着塑胶布。[l]刚好是一个人的宽度。"

# game/day 9.rpy:1858
translate chinese_simplified shin09_cpr_f6ddc1da:

    # extend "but is that a bother for you?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 深_m_03.ks (KS 1277-1279)
    extend "「那时候，似乎刚好孝之助从附近经过。[l]结果他就拍了我睡觉的样子。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:1859
translate chinese_simplified shin09_cpr_86df0c82:

    # fn "「No, not at all!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 深_m_03.ks (KS 1282-1282)
    fn "「啊。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:1863
translate chinese_simplified shin09_cpr_9b612d2d:

    # si "「Then I suppose I will invite you over for a meal?{p} I probably can't compare well to Torahiko's,\n but I can definitely win with Western-style food.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 深_m_03.ks (KS 1288-1289)
    si "「哎，之后他拿那张照片来嘲笑我的时候，我把底片给一起处理掉了就是了。[l]"

# game/day 9.rpy:1864
translate chinese_simplified shin09_cpr_3334d3cc:

    # fn "「Ooh, this is exciting.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 深_m_03.ks (KS 1293-1293)
    fn "「是、是……」"

# game/day 9.rpy:1865
translate chinese_simplified shin09_cpr_a5245af4:

    # si "「You're such a glutton, just like always.」"
    # [原版缩写] 来源: 深_m_03.ks (KS 1295-1296)
    si "连底片都处理掉了……[l]虽然是自做自受，不过孝之助也挺可怜的。"

# game/day 9.rpy:1866
translate chinese_simplified shin09_cpr_eb298dfd:

    # fn "「N-no I'm not.{w} You just invited me over.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 深_m_03.ks (KS 1299-1299)
    fn "「不过既然是那家伙做的，应该只是在开玩笑吧？」"

# game/day 9.rpy:1867
translate chinese_simplified shin09_cpr_53c17ae6:

    # si "「Hmhm.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 深_m_03.ks (KS 1304-1305)
