# game/day 9.rpy:1871
translate chinese_simplified shin09_cpr_77598d0f:

    # si "「Well thanks for your trouble up to this point.{p} And, thanks for worrying about me, {w=.3}[fn]」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 深_m_03.ks (KS 1308-1308)
    si "「是！」"

# game/day 9.rpy:1872
translate chinese_simplified shin09_cpr_32aa378b:

    # fn "「Wait, what?」"
    # [原版缩写] 来源: 深_m_03.ks (KS 1310-1312)
    fn "被平常几乎不会表露感情的深君给这样怒吼，让[漏れ]忍不住马上立正站好。[l]嗯，那样的话真的是太过份了点啦。"

# game/day 9.rpy:1873
translate chinese_simplified shin09_cpr_7a8c7af3:

    # si "「Nothing.{p} Never mind that, is there anything you can't eat?\nAnything you want to request?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 深_m_03.ks (KS 1318-1318)
