    # fn "「But, you seem to be okay.{w} That's good.{w=.3}\n My heart was pounding when I found you.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: extract/orig/深_m_03.ks (KS 1172-1174)
    fn "【fn】\n「But, you seem to be okay. That's good. My heart was pounding when I found you.」"

# game/day 9.rpy:1912
