# game/day 9.rpy:2164
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki09_help_95b64e35:

    # ta "「Who's a green iguana!?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 辰樹_s_05.ks (KS 149)
    ta "「你说谁是绿鬣蜥啊」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2165
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki09_help_6d13a12c:

    # fn "「Well, it'll be okay.{p} He said he'll be here soon.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 辰樹_s_05.ks (KS 151-152)
    fn "「嘛~没事的啦。[l]肯定会来的」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2169
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki09_help_5ec79372:

    # ta "「Really? I don't know about that.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 辰樹_s_05.ks (KS 156)
    ta "「真的假的，[wdt]会变成怎样我可不管哦」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2170
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki09_help_d6c27f8d:

    # "On that day, no matter how much time passed,\nShun-kun never showed up....."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 辰樹_s_05.ks (KS 158)
    "那一天，无论过了多久峻君都没有出现……"

# game/day 9.rpy:2180
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki09_goout_edb62377:

    # fn "「Let's go out and hit on some people.{p} Our summer starts right here!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 辰樹_s_05.ks (KS 166-167)
    fn "「接下来[fn]们就去朝气勃勃地找辣妹搭讪吧。[l][fn]们的夏天现在才开始呢」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2181
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki09_goout_33328d83:

    # who "「Oh, [fn]-kun, is it?{p} Long time no see.{p} If you're looking for Shun, he already left.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 辰樹_s_05.ks (KS 170-171)
    who "「啊是[fn]君啊，好久不见。[l]要找峻的话他出门了哦」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2182
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki09_goout_4cbe89e4:

    # "Huh?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 辰樹_s_05.ks (KS 173)
    "晤？"

# game/day 9.rpy:2183
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki09_goout_19845dde:

    # "Shun-kun's voice is kind of deep...{p}His dad!?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 辰樹_s_05.ks (KS 175)
    "要说是峻君的话声音显得低沉了点……[l]他���爸���？"

# game/day 9.rpy:2184
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki09_goout_e701c3a5:

    # ryo "「Want me to pass on the message?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 辰樹_s_05.ks (KS 178)
    ryo "「要帮忙传话吗？」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2185
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki09_goout_c3f05854:

    # "On the other end of the receiver, I could\nhear giggling."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 辰樹_s_05.ks (KS 180)
    "听筒的对面传来了哧哧的笑声。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2186
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki09_goout_5be8c135:

    # fn "「No,{w=.3} that won't be necessary.{p} Excuse me.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 辰樹_s_05.ks (KS 182-183)
    fn "「不不，不用了。[l]失礼了」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2190
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki09_goout_95ebb0d4:

    # "I was embarrassed as I quickly put the phone down.{p}I feel Tatsu-nii's cold stare behind me."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 辰樹_s_05.ks (KS 186-187)
    "[fn]实在觉得太害羞了，迅速放下了听筒。[l]突然感觉到身后辰兄冰冷的视线。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2191
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki09_goout_89fe2c83:

    # "D-{w=.3}don't look..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 辰樹_s_05.ks (KS 188)
    "别，[wdt]别盯着[fn]……。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2192
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki09_goout_5ed6375a:

    # fn "「Well, seems like Shun-kun went out.{p} Looks like you had nothing to worry about, and since\n there's no other way, how about just us two go out?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 辰樹_s_05.ks (KS 191-193)
    fn "「额呀~~，说是峻君出门了呢。[l]看来没必要替他担心呢，没办法了今天就[fn]们去玩吧」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2196
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki09_goout_1d3b460d:

    # ta "「...Yeah,{w=.3} maybe we can call over Tora.{p} Oh, I'll have to call his number, so you just\n make yourself at home.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 辰樹_s_05.ks (KS 197-199)
    ta "「……也是，把虎那家伙也叫来吧。[l]啊，电话我来打就行了，你就休息下吧」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2197
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki09_goout_2bac8461:

    # "Uu,{w=.3} if there's a hole somewhere,\nI want to hide in it..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 辰樹_s_05.ks (KS 201)
    "呜哇，[wdt]好想找个洞钻进去……"

# game/day 9.rpy:2219
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_71733873:

    # "The once-sunny sky has been covered by clouds.{p}I only really noticed when the sunlight had\nstopped shining down on me."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 10)
    "【我】原本极为晴朗的天空，不知何时已经被大量乌云覆盖。当在村中散步的我注意到这件事时，已经有一段时间没看到那刺眼的阳光了。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2220
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_40850118:

    # "There's a rumble of thunder in the distance."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 14)
    "【我】远方开始响起一阵阵的雷声。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2221
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_9a396553:

    # fn "「Uh-oh,{w=.3} looks like it's going to rain...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 17)
    fn "【我】「晤哇，总觉得好像会下雨的样子……」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2222
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_ef1da038:

    # "I unintentionally mutter to myself at the sound.{p}It was sunny when I set out this morning,{w=.3}\nso I didn't think to bring an umbrella with me."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 19)
    "【我】听到那不祥的声音，我忍不住自言自语起来。中午前还是大晴天的，我当然也就没有带伞。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2223
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_182ebdf7:

    # "I look up at the sky,\nwondering whether I can get home before it\nstarts to rain."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 22)
    "【我】在开始下雨前赶得回家吗……我一边看着天空一边这样想着。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2227
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_4d612970:

    # "A raindrop lands on my right hand."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 28)
    "【我】这时雨滴已经滴到了我的右手上。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2232
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_d5b5a518:

    # fn "「Damn it!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 33)
    fn "【我】「糟了！」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2233
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_843aa1c0:

    # "As I start to run,{w=.3}\nthe rain strengthens,\nas though it were mocking me.{w}{nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 35)
    "【我】就像是要嘲笑连忙开始急奔的我似的，雨一下子就变得非常的大。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2236
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_3d1a9ff7:

    # extend "{w=.01}{nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 36)
    extend "【我】"

# game/day 9.rpy:2239
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_e26bd1b6:

    # "My shoes make a wet squelching sound with each step,{w=.3}\nbut there's nothing I can do about it."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 45)
    "【我】脚踩在地上时鞋子内的水都会被挤得发出声音，虽然感觉很不舒服可是也没办法。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2240
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_a5b0e39e:

    # "Earlier, I was thinking about\ngoing to the candy store,{w=.3}\nbut it would be a pain to go there now."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 48)
    "【我】刚刚虽然想说先回零食店去躲一下雨好了，但是现在这样全身湿透了去的话会给他们造成麻烦的。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2241
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_86d8a8f5:

    # "It seems the best course\nof action would be to go home."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 50)
    "【我】现在还是乖乖地回家去好了。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2242
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_611209b7:

    # "...I'd like to think that this is giving\nme a break from the summer heat,\nbut I'm actually getting pretty cold."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 52)
    "【我】……虽然这么想，可是刚开始下雨时身体很热还说那样刚好，现在一直淋雨结果身体就开始有点发冷了。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2243
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_d257bb8a:

    # "As I think about that, I rub my arms."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 56)
    "【我】我用双手抱住胸口取暖，开始思考着。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2244
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_c7919fc0:

    # "I want to get home and take a nice, warm bath."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 58)
    "【我】想要尽可能早点回到家去洗澡。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2245
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_2d815191:

    # "It'd be earlier than usual,\nbut given the pitiful state I'm in,\nI don't think Grandpa would mind."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 60)
    "【我】虽然比平常要早很多，不过看到这个惨状，爷爷一定也会觉得该洗吧。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2246
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_73c2070a:

    # "While I'm walking along, thinking warm thoughts,{w=.3}\nthe bus stop suddenly enters my field of vision."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 63)
    "【我】我一边妄想一边往前走着，突然注意到我前面不远处就是公车站了。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2247
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_e3dacb46:

    # "...Hm, the bus stop?{p}That means shelter, doesn't it?{p}I can get out of the rain!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 65)
    "【我】……嗯，公车站？它旁边就是等车处不是了吗。这样就可以在那里躲雨了！"

# game/day 9.rpy:2248
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_f16b9dd5:

    # "I remember a shelter being next to the bus stop,{w=.3}\ncausing my spirits to rise.\nUnable to help myself, I half-jog towards it."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 69)
    "【我】想到公车站旁边就有等车处可以躲雨，我马上就高兴了起来。压抑不住心中的期待，我立刻往公车站小跑步跑了过去。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2256
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_726218f2:

    # "Whew, saved.{w} Now I'll just wait out the rain."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 78)
    "【我】呼，得救了。总之就先在这里等雨变小吧。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2257
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_c5b68f13:

    # "Arriving at my destination,{w=.3}\nI put my hand on the steel door to enter."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 80)
    "【我】好容易终于到了目的地的我，正准备要进去等车处，把手放到铁门的上时，突然发现透过窗户看过去，里面已经有人了。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2258
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_a9f15e47:

    # "It's then that I meet eyes with\nthe person who got here before me."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 89)
    "【我】打开门后，我向坐在里面板凳上的柔一打招呼。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2259
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_d1c5ce21:

    # fn "「Oh, Juuichi-san.{w} Hello.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 85)
    fn "【我】「啊，柔一。午安。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2263
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_be65c2fb:

    # "I open the door and greet Juuichi-san,\nwho was already sitting inside."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 95)
    "【柔一】「[西村]吗。雨下得还真大啊。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2268
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_946b0aeb:

    # ju "「[ln]?{p} Seems like it's really coming down.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 98)
    ju "【我】「真的呢。突然就下起雨来还真麻竿，虽然我是人类，但也感觉变得像淋湿的老鼠似的。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2269
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_46f13e78:

    # fn "「Yeah, it is.{p} It caught me by surprise.{w=.3}\n I know I'm human, but I feel like a drowned rat...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 105)
    fn "【柔一】【沉默】"

# game/day 9.rpy:2273
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_1952fb49:

    # ju "「...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 107)
    ju "【我】柔一沉默了起来。……嗯，我还以为这样的讲法听起来还算风趣的说。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2274
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_b386b63d:

    # "He doesn't say a word.{p}...Hmm,{w=.3} I did try to say something witty."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 111)
    "【我】不过很可惜，看来柔一一点都没感觉的样子。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2275
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_a6805e86:

    # "Unfortunately, it seems Juuichi-san is not amused."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 114)
    "【柔一】「……总之先进来擦乾身体吧。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2276
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_6e6a16b9:

    # ju "「...Anyway, come in and dry yourself off.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 117)
    ju "【我】「那我���恭敬不如从命了。打扰了。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2277
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_22f2d3ed:

    # fn "「If you insist.{p} Excuse the intrusion.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 122)
    fn "【柔一】「不用在意，这里又不是我家。没什么好客气的。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2281
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_f5f5e0b6:

    # ju "「It's not like this is my house.{p} There's no need to be so polite.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 124)
    ju "【我】说起来确实是那样啦。不过，两个人一起待在这个狭小的空间里，不知怎地有种这是柔一的地盘的奇特感觉。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2282
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_93f2926b:

    # "He does have a point.{p}But, with the two of us in the shelter,{w=.3}\nit strangely seems like it's Juuichi-san's space."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 128)
    "【我】我进去里面后，想说可以先把湿掉的汗衫给脱下来。虽然没有带可以擦乾的东西，不过把它拧乾后勉强还可以用用。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2283
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_1f33be3f:

    # "I step inside, and decide to take off my wet shirt.{p}I don't have anything to dry off with,{w=.3}\nso should I just wring my shirt out and use that?"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 133)
    "【我】「那就不好意思了。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2284
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_93b6af3c:

    # fn "「Excuse me for a second.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 137)
    fn "【我】我背向柔一，把湿透后黏在衣服上的汗衫给慢慢脱了下来。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2288
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_df58841d:

    # "I turn my back to him,\nand try to take off the shirt\nthat's stuck to my skin."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 140)
    "【我】……衣服湿掉之后，为什么会这么难脱啊。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2289
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_747bd541:

    # "...I wonder why wet clothes\nare so difficult to get off."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 142)
    "【我】平常都是抓住汗衫下摆往上拉来脱的，但现在卡在肩膀的部位没办法再往上拉了。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2290
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_d6beb6e2:

    # "I try lifting the hem of my shirt,{w=.3}\nbut it gets stuck on my shoulders."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 145)
    "【我】该怎么说，现在的我看起来简直像是穿着拘束衣的犯人似的。而且还露出肚脐。……这也未免太丢脸了。"

