    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 590)
    "【柔一】「哎，没关系。我本来也是容易胖的体质就是了。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2518
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_b9a7aefc:

    # ju "「The heavier you are,\n the harder it is to get thrown,\n and your opponents have a harder time when pinned.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 592)
    ju "【我】柔一用大姆指揉了揉下巴。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2519
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_5459f04f:

    # ju "「Being physically large\n also intimidates the opponent, too.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 575)
    ju "【柔一】能增加威压感的话，也能够给对手的精神造成压力。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2520
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_bd6abf45:

    # ju "「There are a surprising number of times where\n weight can be a weapon, [ln].」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 595)
    ju "【柔一】「……而且，我也确实不讨厌甜食啦。黑井也常常做些好东西。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2521
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_464b58c3:

    # fn "「...I'm sorry.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 599)
    fn "【我】「深？」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2522
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_def76584:

    # "It was inappropriate for me to\nassume he was eating too many sweets.{p}I meekly bow my head."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 584)
    "【我】把这当成卡路里摄取过量是我失言了。我老实地低下头。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2526
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_0bba0932:

    # ju "「Don't worry about it.{p} I put on weight easily, anyway.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 604)
    ju "【柔一】「啊啊。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2527
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_0f5e7f0a:

    # "He scratches his chin with a thumb."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 606)
    "【我】虎彦很擅长做菜这我是知道啦，不过原来深也很会做甜点吗……晤，这��就没听说了。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2528
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_203bd979:

    # ju "「...Besides,{w=.3} you're not wrong\n about me liking sweets.{p} Kuroi often makes them for me.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 611)
    ju "【我】「我也想吃吃看深做的甜点说……」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2529
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_2f77e505:

    # fn "「Shin-kun?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 606)
    fn "【我】虎彦很擅长做菜这我是知道啦，不过原来深也很会做甜点吗……晤，这就�_没听说了。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2533
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_40f2a2a4:

    # ju "「Yeah.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 604)
    ju "【柔一】啊啊。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2534
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_fb6d87da:

    # "I knew Torahiko cooks things for him,{w=.3}\nbut Shin-kun makes sweets for him, too...?{p}Wow, I had no idea."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 650)
    "【我】我随口问问的问题，柔一倒是很认真地回答了。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2535
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_9a0a5b13:

    # fn "「I'd like to try his sweets, sometime...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 611)
    fn "【我】、『我也想吃吃看深做的甜点说……』"

# game/day 9.rpy:2536
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_6d35c715:

    # ju "「Why don't you ask him?{p} I'm sure he will, if he's in the right mood.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 614)
    ju "【柔一】、『跟他本人说说看如何？他要是心情好的话或许会做给你吃。』"

# game/day 9.rpy:2537
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_157514ce:

    # "Ah, that's the hard part, though.{p}I'll wait and see how things go,\nthe next time I see him."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 621)
    "【我】「深的话，总觉得会做出非常精緻的甜食的感觉呢。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2538
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_a04bcac3:

    # fn "「He makes awfully dainty sweets, doesn't he?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 624)
    fn "【柔一】「要说精緻吗嘛……不如说是给人一种，仔细考虑过吃的人的心情才做出来的感觉。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2539
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_a0d17265:

    # ju "「I wouldn't say that...{w=.3}\n {nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 628)
    ju "【我】「咦，是那样吗？感觉有点意外呢。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2541
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_33a0ceb8:

    # extend "They have the impression of somebody who thinks\n carefully about what goes in them.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 624-625)
    extend "【柔一】「要说精致吗嘛……[wdt]不如说是给人一种，仔细考虑过吃的人的心情才做出来的感觉。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2542
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_6e6e1d49:

    # fn "「Huh, really?{p} I wasn't expecting that.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 617)
    fn "【我】嗯，这大概就是最需要注意的地方了吧。下次仔细观察深的心情再伺机拜託他好了。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2543
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_de0d0907:

    # "I had the idea that he drew patterns on the plate,{w=.3}\nor maybe decorated his sweets...{p}I guess I was wrong."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 630)
    "【我】深给人的印象，比较像是会仔细在盘子上绘图、给糖果做造型等等，做这一类精緻装饰的感觉……看来似乎不是这样呢。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2547
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_c17b0250:

    # ju "「If I'm with him,{w=.3} he usually\n mixes honey into his sweets.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 637)
    ju "【柔一】、「如果是做给我吃的话，大部分都会掺蜂蜜进去。而且会事先跟我说会做得比平常还要甜。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2548
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_e5eb19aa:

    # ju "「He makes things sweeter than usual,\n after I mentioned I like them that way.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 640)
    ju "【我】深在这种地方会这么认真啊。那，事前先跟深提过的话，或许他也会帮我做我喜欢的甜点也不一定。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2549
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_6208abaf:

    # "Shin-kun will do things like that?{p}I wonder if he'd make my favorite sweets\nif I said something beforehand."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 644)
    "【我】说起来，果然柔一很喜欢甜食……好像应该说喜欢蜂蜜才对。这点真的很像熊人呢。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2550
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_a76a7a79:

    # "He loves sweet things... Rather, honey?{p}I wonder if all bears are like that."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 648)
    "【我】、「那样的话，虎彦和深谁做的甜点比较好吃呢？」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2551
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_e8fa39e3:

    # fn "「So who makes better sweets,\n Torahiko or Shin-kun?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 653)
    fn "【柔一】【严肃地回答】"

# game/day 9.rpy:2552
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_00e99cf2:

    # "I was a bit hesitant to ask that question.{w=.3}\nJuuichi replies with a heavy growl."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 650)
    "【我】我随口问问的问题，柔一倒是很认真地回答了。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2557
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_9e20ca6e:

    # ju "「I'd say...{w} Kuroi?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 657)
    ju "【柔一】、「这个嘛……黑井吧，我想。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2558
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_fb9ab903:

    # fn "「Really? I thought Torahiko was the best chef\n out of our group, though.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 660)
    fn "【我】、「我还以为虎彦是我中最会做菜的人的说。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2562
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_9eb98620:

    # ju "「That's just my opinion.{p} Tora is definitely an above-average chef.{p} It's rare that he makes something that I can't eat.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 665)
    ju "【柔一】、「要说的话这也只是我的个人意见啦。不过该怎么说，虎那家伙是平均来说各种东西都做得很好。他做的东西几乎没有什么是让人不想吃的。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2563
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_6427ca66:

    # ju "「On the other hand, Kuroi precisely caters to\n personal tastes. Depending on the person, I think\n Kuroi would have a more professional evaluation.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 671)
    ju "【柔一】相比之下黑井则是，会针对各人的喜好去做合适的甜点。虽然每个人看法可能不同，不过就业余的来说，我会觉得黑井做的比较合味口。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2564
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_18716a05:

    # fn "「Oh, I see.{w} That might be true.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 676)
    fn "【我】、「啊，原来如此。确实有可能是这样呢。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2568
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_373b4886:

    # ju "「...Don't tell Tora I said that, okay?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 681)
    ju "【柔一】、『……不要跟虎说喔？』"

# game/day 9.rpy:2569
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_6c94017c:

    # fn "「I won't.{w} If I did,{w=.3}\n it'd probably make him depressed.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 681)
    fn "【柔一】：「……不要跟虎说喔？」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2578
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_bb260fac:

    # "It's not hard to imagine Torahiko looking at me\nwith his ears down, tail drooping, and sad eyes."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 684)
    "【我】、『我知道的啦。要是听到这些话，虎彦一定会觉得气馁的吧。』"

# game/day 9.rpy:2579
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_4e858ed4:

    # "He's a feline, but for some reason\nhe looks more like an abandoned puppy."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 694)
    "【我】耳朵向后倒，尾巴下垂，用悲伤的眼神看着这里的虎彦的样子，算是挺容易想像的。虽然是猫科，不过不知怎地却像是被抛弃的小狗似的。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2590
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_0d29128a:

    # fn "「Oh,{w=.3} sounds like the rain is letting up.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 706)
    fn "【我】、「啊，雨好像变小了的样子。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2591
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_4f8da5c9:

    # ju "「You're right.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 709)
    ju "【柔一】确实呢。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2592
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_a26c530b:

    # "I stand up,{w=.3}\n{nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 711)
    "【我】我从板凳上站了起来，打开玻璃窗把手伸到外面去接雨。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2594
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_9442b416:

    # extend "pull open the door,\nand reach out with my palm."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 716)
    extend "【我】刚刚的大雨简直像骗人的似的。虽然手上还是有些细小的雨滴滴落，不过这种程度回去也不会被淋湿了。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2598
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_ebacda9f:

    # "It feels as if the rain from earlier never happened."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 720)
    "【我】把头伸出去往天空一看，在乌云间已经可以隐约看到蓝色的天空了。这样看来雨完全停下也只是时间问题而已了。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2599
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_554e15de:

    # "There are a few spots here and there,{w=.3}\nbut I think I can make it\nhome without getting soaked."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 723)
    "【我】柔一也站起来走到我的身旁，一起看着天空云的状况。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2600
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_f5d87cfa:

    # "I poke my head through the door,\nand look up at the sky."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 720-721)
    "把头伸出去往天空一看，[wdt]在乌云间已经可以隐约看到蓝色的天空了。[l]这样看来雨完全停下也只是时间问题而已了。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2601
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_4ea0a802:

    # "I can see a patch of blue through the clouds.\nIt's only a matter of time\nbefore the rain stops completely."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 732)
    "【我】、「确实呢。……唉，没想到会遇上这种惨事。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2602
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_95096283:

    # "Juuichi-san gets up,{w=.3}\nand takes a look at the clouds, too."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 735)
    "【柔一】平常坏事做多了的关系吧。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2606
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_1742f0d3:

    # ju "「The rain will stop soon, at this rate.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 752)
    ju "【我】说着还轻轻敲了我的头几下。柔一的手又大又温暖，感觉就像是父亲的手似的。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2607
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_f68f69b6:

    # fn "「You're right.{p} ...Man,{w=.3} I did not have a good time out there.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 756)
    fn "【我】……而且被这样子对待，害我一下子连抱怨的力气也没有了。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2608
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_5155e724:

    # ju "「You've got some bad habits, don't you?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 750)
    ju "【柔一】【轻轻敲我的头】"

# game/day 9.rpy:2609
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_12d2dc13:

    # fn "「I'm not as bad as Torahiko or Kounosuke.{p} ...Wait, that wasn't very nice!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 750)
    fn "【柔一】……抱歉啊。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2616
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_9129fdfb:

    # "When I raise my voice in protest,{w=.3}\nthe corners of Juuichi's mouth lift slightly."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 694)
    "【我】耳朵向后倒，尾巴下垂，用悲伤的眼神看着这里的虎彦的样子，倒是挺容易想像的。虽然是猫科，不过不知怎地却像是被抛弃的小狗似的。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2617
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_449df542:

    # ju "「...Sorry.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 698)
    ju "【我】"

# game/day 9.rpy:2618
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_63c96d55:

    # "He pats me on the head a few times.{p}His large hands are warm,{w=.3}\nalmost like a father's."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 750)
    "【柔一】、【轻轻敲我的头】"

# game/day 9.rpy:2619
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_17271bff:

    # "...When he does that,{w=.3}\nI lose the energy to complain."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 756)
    "【我】……而且被这样子对待，害我一下子连抱怨的力气也没有了。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2620
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_talk_c6aadabe:

    # ju "「You can hold on to that jacket for now,\n so leave it on.{p} You don't want to wear wet clothes home, do you?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 760)
    ju "【柔一】外套就借你了，你就穿回家去吧。现在也不会想把湿掉的衣服穿回去吧？」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2635
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_borrow_439e5fce:

    # fn "「Thanks,{w=.3} I'll hold on to it.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 779)
    fn "【我】、『不好意思，那我就借回家了。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2636
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_borrow_3c1a5a4f:

    # "I decide to do as he says, and borrow his jersey.{p}Since he's letting me use it,{w=.3}\nI'll make sure to wash it and get it back to him."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 781)
    "【我】我就老实地把柔一的运动外套给借回去了。虽然只是借给我很短的一段时间，不过这种情况还是好好地洗过之后再还给对方会比较好。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2637
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_borrow_b8c532dd:

    # "...Besides, he's right.{p}I don't want to wear my soaking-wet shirt again."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 785)
    "【我】……而且，就跟柔一说的一样，要把湿掉的汗衫给穿回去还真的挺难过的。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2638
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_borrow_27ad6acc:

    # ju "「So your torso is covered,{w=.3}\n but are you going to put your pants on?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 789)
    ju "【柔一】上衣这样是没问题了，裤子可也要好好地穿回去喔？」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2639
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_borrow_6a26b7f2:

    # fn "「Of course I won't forget my pants!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 792)
    fn "【我】、「啊差点就把裤子给忘了！」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2640
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_borrow_51310c3b:

    # "It's unpleasant, but I don't have a choice.{p}I don't want to get in trouble with the police,{w=.3}\nso I force myself to put my wet pants back on."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 794)
    "【我】虽然湿裤子穿起来不舒服，不过这时候也没办法了。我可不想被警察给带走，只好放弃老实地把裤子给硬穿回去。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2641
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_borrow_c17fdd08:

    # "...Eugh, I need to take a bath when I get home."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 798)
    "【我】……呜呜，果然回家后是不洗澡不行了。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2645
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_borrow_166578fe:

    # "As I'm thinking about that,{w=.3}\nJuuichi-san and I both head home."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 802)
    "【我】我一边想着这种事，一边和柔一一起踏上了回家的路。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2654
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_return_6e6151f2:

    # fn "「Nah, I'll be fine.{p} Thanks for letting me borrow the jersey.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 813)
    fn "【我】不用啦，没关系的。谢谢你借我外套。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2655
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_return_98dbf26a:

    # "I don't want to impose on him that much.{p}I take off the jacket, fold it up,{w=.3}\nand hand it back to him."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 815)
    "【我】可不能再继续给柔一添麻烦了。我把披在身上的外套脱了下来，稍微折了一下还给柔一。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2656
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_return_f64d55e2:

    # ju "「...Hm,{w=.3} I see.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 820)
    ju "【柔一】「……嗯，这样啊。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2660
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_return_edec64f2:

    # "Juuichi-san doesn't press the issue further.{p}{nw}"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 824)
    "【我】柔一也没有再多说什么，就把我递过去的外套穿了起来。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2663
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_return_9f94f783:

    # extend "He takes back the jersey, and puts it on."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 828)
    extend "【柔一】那么，差不多也该回去了。」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2665
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_return_7c14a816:

    # ju "「All right, let's head home.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 832)
    ju "【我】说完后柔一就从等车处走了出去。我连忙想要跟上去，却在这时候才想起来自己现在还只穿着一条内裤。"

# game/day 9.rpy:2669
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_return_f3ad108f:

    # "As he says that, he exits the waiting area.{p}I go to follow him,{w=.3}\nthen remember that I'm only wearing my underwear."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 837)
    "【我】、「柔一，我马上穿衣服请等我一下啦――！」"

# game/day 9.rpy:2670
translate chinese_simplified juuichi09_return_32246627:

    # fn "「Juuichi-saaan,{w=.3} please wait!\nI'm wearing clothes now!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 柔一_m_04.ks (KS 837)
    fn "【我】、『柔一，我马上穿衣服请等我一下啦――！』"

